Without BC: with 2D case with peridic boundary conditions

python extract_data_spatial_order_v2.py -ups kokkos-xy-scalar.ups -levels 3 -nsteps 1 -suspath ~/CODE_11_09_17/Uintah/debug/StandAlone/ -vars "phi,phi_mms" -dire "x" -var_mms "phi_mms"

With BC:

With Dirichlet for y faces, Neumann for z faces, and handoff for x faces

python extract_data_spatial_order_v2.py -ups kokkos-xy-scalar-handoff.ups -levels 3 -nsteps 1 -suspath ~/CODE_11_09_17/Uintah/debug/StandAlone/ -vars "phi,phi_mms" -dire "x" -var_mms "phi_mms"




